Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.54,0:00:19.42,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}It's come to the point where I just want to hoard all your words
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.42,0:00:25.39,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Even the ramblings from your travels are treasures to me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.39,0:00:28.57,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Whether I sketch or erase it's all torn away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.57,0:00:32.12,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}That's the price I pay for my awakening
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.12,0:00:37.68,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Or my daydream's tricking me and I'm still lost in the unknown
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.68,0:00:40.85,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Illuminated by the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:44.02,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Your figure casts a shadow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:47.15,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}And when that silhouette wavers slightly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.15,0:00:49.99,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}That happens to be my cue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:56.95,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}I wish this were fiction but slow motion is how it begins
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.26,0:01:02.88,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}If the visceral warmth and traces you left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:09.05,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Are protecting someone's future, I'll play the warrior
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.05,0:01:12.59,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Amidst pain and sorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.59,0:01:15.59,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}I'll conquer my fears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.59,0:01:18.64,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}It's a paradox of life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.64,0:01:21.10,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Or perhaps god's algorithm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.39,0:01:24.85,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}When our tactics overcome
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.85,0:01:29.61,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}We'll be laughing
