Dialogue: 5,0:01:37.75,0:01:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When were ya born?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:39.38,0:01:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who gave birth to ya?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:41.34,0:01:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, at the wake.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:43.92,0:01:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother scanned Mio there.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:46.73,0:01:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Later that night...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:51.80,0:01:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I was born in the cave.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:55.82,0:02:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,When ya say "Mother," \Nya mean Haine in Shiori's body, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:01.58,0:02:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:05.05,0:02:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Did ya cut the brakes on Mio's bike?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:07.76,0:02:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:08.73,0:02:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,To kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.07,0:02:13.28,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(914,318)\fscx123\fscy123\frz-12.58\fax0.23\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\b1\c&H120E0A&\blur1}N{\c&H120D09&}urse's {\c&H120D08&}Office
Dialogue: 5,0:02:11.68,0:02:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Not necessarily.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:13.75,0:02:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just more convenient if ya were in the hospital.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:18.49,0:02:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more convenient to kill Mio in the hospital and take her place?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:22.96,0:02:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, since Dr. Hishigata is an ally of the shadows.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:27.54,0:02:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that Haine's order?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:30.16,0:02:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I just wanted to do that.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:33.65,0:02:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But I failed.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:35.50,0:02:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that they were gonna make a shadow of Mio.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:40.63,0:02:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Tokiko.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:42.42,0:02:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know why I wanted to kill her anymore.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:46.90,0:02:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Haine created ya to find Ushio's shadow.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:51.86,0:02:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She {\i1}is{\i0} a traitor.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:54.01,0:02:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't copy people.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:56.16,0:02:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Can ya do it?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:58.30,0:03:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two types of copying.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:00.70,0:03:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking the form of the person we copy, or giving birth to a new shadow.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:08.08,0:03:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving birth?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:09.34,0:03:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We children can give birth to a new shadow only once.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:14.44,0:03:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"Children"?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:16.12,0:03:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Haine can give birth as many times as she wants,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:18.16,0:03:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but since she's become weak, it's no longer easy fer her.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:23.24,0:03:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadows at the grandchild level can't give birth.
