Dialogue: 5,0:03:39.43,0:03:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I have six more days to live, although I don't really care.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:45.28,0:03:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I know.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:47.73,0:03:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Shin.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:49.56,0:03:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have much useful information.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:52.16,0:03:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:53.59,0:03:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Ya don't need to apologize!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:56.86,0:03:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's a shadow, Sou.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:59.64,0:04:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Uh, but...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:03.71,0:04:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sou?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:05.98,0:04:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:07.43,0:04:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is confusing!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:09.52,0:04:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Haine needs to consume a lot\N of people for her to be revived.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:14.19,0:04:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She's giving birth to build an army for that.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:17.33,0:04:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad and I tried to revive Haine for my mother's sake.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:23.04,0:04:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought she needed the meals for that purpose,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:29.02,0:04:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but they had a different objective.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:33.20,0:04:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And the old man knew everything?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:36.27,0:04:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:37.90,0:04:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't care if we all die.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:41.21,0:04:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:43.27,0:04:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to take it in,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:45.67,0:04:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but Dr. Hishigata must know Haine's true objective.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:50.34,0:04:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm meeting him tonight at 10 o'clock.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:56.20,0:04:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then we know what to do next.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:59.70,0:05:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to Hishigata Clinic.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:03.09,0:05:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so itchy!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:04.66,0:05:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There are so many mosquitoes here!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:07.12,0:05:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect Mio.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:10.33,0:05:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that an order?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:12.94,0:05:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno if I'd call it that...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:14.78,0:05:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:18.35,0:05:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Shin, are ya afraid of me?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:21.89,0:05:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer so far away.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:23.58,0:05:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'd be lying if I said no.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:27.29,0:05:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya killed me over and over, ya know.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:29.88,0:05:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That was in another world.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:32.65,0:05:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't killed anyone yet.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:36.72,0:05:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask ya something too?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:40.33,0:05:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:42.14,0:05:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Did ya have a girlfriend in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:44.77,0:05:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl—
Dialogue: 5,0:05:44.77,0:05:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Girlfriend?!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:46.62,0:05:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are ya asking him?!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:49.21,0:05:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He sometimes speaks like they do in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:52.96,0:05:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't it suspicious?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:54.73,0:05:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I ain't got a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:56.43,0:05:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,People just don't understand the Wakayama dialect in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:59.51,0:06:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I try to blend in with the locals.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:03.89,0:06:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I was just joking.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:07.03,0:06:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Have ya ever wondered why I don't call ya "Brother"?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:19.35,0:06:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, I'll follow yer order and protect Mio.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:23.27,0:06:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But yer the only one who can really protect Mio.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:30.09,0:06:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know what she's talking about!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:33.04,0:06:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just go, Shin!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:34.64,0:06:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
