Dialogue: 5,0:06:50.95,0:06:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's open.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:55.02,0:06:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:56.91,0:06:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything in our house is gone.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:59.68,0:07:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Our rooms are empty too.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:02.61,0:07:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Desks, closets, beds... everything.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:06.86,0:07:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Nagumo, is this...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:09.21,0:07:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:10.89,0:07:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, there aren't any human stains.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:13.31,0:07:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that only things were erased.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:16.19,0:07:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there something that they didn't want us to see?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:20.21,0:07:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Although it seems like they erased everything.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:23.13,0:07:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They had to hide something but didn't know where it was.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:28.93,0:07:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my impression.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:31.52,0:07:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This has to be my old man!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:33.62,0:07:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he's not here!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:36.25,0:07:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Our mom is gone too.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:37.77,0:07:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is happening?!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:39.90,0:07:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:43.31,0:07:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya felt a shadow over here, didn't ya, Ushio?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:46.75,0:07:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:47.91,0:07:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:49.24,0:07:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't squeeze so hard! It cuts off the blood flow!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:52.69,0:07:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are ya scared?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:53.45,0:07:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Of course I'm scared!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:56.31,0:07:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate hospitals at night...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:00.43,0:08:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear something.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:09.80,0:08:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not coming.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:10.89,0:08:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:12.63,0:08:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something stuck in the door at the basement level?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:17.17,0:08:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullet holes.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:19.08,0:08:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like there was a fight here.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:22.43,0:08:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:23.76,0:08:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I sense shadows below us.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:26.30,0:08:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's in the basement?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:29.75,0:08:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The morgue.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:31.55,0:08:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The morgue?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:33.13,0:08:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:35.02,0:08:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing down there is Ushio's body that Dad didn't cremate.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:40.70,0:08:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:41.82,0:08:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it ain't scary if it's my body.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:43.87,0:08:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it works?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:45.43,0:08:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeling fear shows that your survival instincts are functioning properly.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:50.25,0:08:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing to be ashamed of.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:52.27,0:08:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadows are scarier than ghosts.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:55.25,0:08:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Brace yourselves.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:06.49,0:09:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Mom's wheelchair.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:08.69,0:09:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's it here?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:11.03,0:09:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:16.74,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(601,324)\fscx77\fscy77\frz21.05\fnSchuboiseHandwrite\fsp2\b1\c&H5D4E32&\blur0.8}Morgue
Dialogue: 5,0:09:16.74,0:09:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Did ya see its face?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:18.59,0:09:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:38.14,0:09:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-There's nothing here.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:52.00,0:09:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:53.74,0:09:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea this place was under our house.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:58.22,0:09:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:59.66,0:10:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio's body was here?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:02.17,0:10:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:03.55,0:10:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio could've recovered if she was able to scan the original.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:08.21,0:10:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They must've decided it was best not to leave it here until tomorrow.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:16.64,0:10:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to restart?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:18.35,0:10:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, let's keep going.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:20.74,0:10:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to find Sou's parents.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:24.27,0:10:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:26.01,0:10:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this passage, Toki?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:28.78,0:10:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It connects to Hiruko's grotto.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:31.61,0:10:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There was an entrance here.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:33.58,0:10:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We used it to bring meals to Haine.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:37.53,0:10:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a different route than the old path from the old clinic.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:41.84,0:10:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel a subtle presence of shadows.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:44.82,0:10:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The one from earlier must've gone in here.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:50.87,0:10:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's close.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:52.72,0:10:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost upon it.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:11.44,0:11:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:17.95,0:11:17.95,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.95,0:11:21.79,title,,0,0,0,,{\bord5\c&HC0A038&\blur7}Summer Time Rendering
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.95,0:11:21.79,title,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}Summer Time Rendering
Dialogue: 5,0:11:19.03,0:11:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:22.47,0:11:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:23.12,0:11:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't shoot her!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:24.96,0:11:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But yer dad will die!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:31.45,0:11:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:33.19,0:11:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Sou.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:35.42,0:11:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring her back.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:43.60,0:11:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:51.87,0:11:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not breathing.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:09.42,0:12:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemme do it!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:14.86,0:12:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, old man! Don't die on me!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:18.71,0:12:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go without explaining yerself!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:23.46,0:12:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, old man!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:38.00,0:12:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sou?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:40.49,0:12:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop keeping secrets.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:43.04,0:12:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We're family.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:45.58,0:12:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Chitose... your mother?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:49.41,0:12:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I cut her link with Haine.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:51.42,0:12:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll wake up soon.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:54.30,0:12:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:55.85,0:12:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:57.83,0:13:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd reach this point so soon.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:01.53,0:13:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So Haine must've thought...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:04.88,0:13:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'd talk.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:08.22,0:13:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No point in hiding anything.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:10.07,0:13:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We can just copy yer data.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:13.92,0:13:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokiko, kill them.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:16.73,0:13:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:17.65,0:13:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:19.81,0:13:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If you kill them, Haine will trust me again.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:24.91,0:13:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Dad.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:27.03,0:13:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya got it all wrong.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:28.86,0:13:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They have no intention of keeping their promises.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:34.44,0:13:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so disappointed in you, Tokiko.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:38.92,0:13:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Step back, Sou.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:40.33,0:13:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Your gun is too close.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:50.12,0:13:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:53.42,0:13:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What... the...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:58.71,0:13:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:01.49,0:14:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:04.52,0:14:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Do ya think they'll be okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:07.70,0:14:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:09.51,0:14:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They've got Ushio and Ms. Nagumo, plus yer shadow.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:14.63,0:14:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my biggest worry!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:16.96,0:14:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I still can't trust that thing.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:19.96,0:14:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised ya let it copy ya.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:23.91,0:14:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,When a shadow copies ya, it sees yer whole body and heart.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:30.56,0:14:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:31.92,0:14:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted ya to know all of me.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:35.81,0:14:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I can't believe ya can say that with a straight face!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:41.60,0:14:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done keeping secrets.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:47.05,0:14:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:49.58,0:14:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do ya trust me a bit now?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:53.28,0:14:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:56.48,0:14:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:58.01,0:15:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya can copy me if ya don't believe my words.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:00.63,0:15:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Never.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:04.45,0:15:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna know what's in yer heart.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:09.03,0:15:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sou!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:10.43,0:15:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya shot Tokiko!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:11.89,0:15:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How could ya?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:15.35,0:15:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:16.35,0:15:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya old fool!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:18.03,0:15:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing with people's lives...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:20.86,0:15:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:24.18,0:15:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't ya a doctor?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:27.03,0:15:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How can a doctor talk about killing so easily?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:30.59,0:15:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:35.24,0:15:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So ya won't say anything.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:37.87,0:15:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:39.80,0:15:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio, do it.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:51.28,0:15:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't copy him.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:52.92,0:15:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He has immunity.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:55.60,0:15:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:56.91,0:15:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll have to make him talk.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:58.09,0:15:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:59.25,0:16:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:00.81,0:16:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't copy me?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:03.90,0:16:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya already had a shadow, but it died.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:09.09,0:16:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,People like y'all have immunity and can't be copied again.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:14.27,0:16:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:16.19,0:16:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My shadow can't be created?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:21.84,0:16:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:27.97,0:16:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:29.43,0:16:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitose...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:31.59,0:16:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it all for, then?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:38.31,0:16:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Negoro.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:43.76,0:16:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, I'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:47.90,0:16:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I got what I came for.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:53.62,0:16:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She's out of range.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:55.36,0:16:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, I have a message from Shide.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:58.63,0:17:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"We appreciate the Hishigata family for the support you provided.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:02.46,0:17:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it's over now.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:05.01,0:17:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care."
Dialogue: 5,0:17:07.80,0:17:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I also have a message for Ajiro Shinpei.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:11.02,0:17:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"It seems you didn't die.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:13.71,0:17:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fed up with your stubbornness.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:16.33,0:17:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing you can do.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:19.13,0:17:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything will end in two days."
Dialogue: 5,0:17:22.71,0:17:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, dammit!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:23.98,0:17:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:28.89,0:17:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go after her.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:30.45,0:17:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:32.22,0:17:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She was using Ushio's body as bait to lure us in.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:36.46,0:17:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Bringing up the time limit was an attempt to provoke us.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:40.99,0:17:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If we take the bait, we're done.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:42.46,0:17:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't just let it go, Shinpei!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:45.60,0:17:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the shadow we saw earlier!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:49.61,0:17:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Sis.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:51.81,0:17:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shin feels the worst about this.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:56.87,0:18:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya can't just let yer emotions drive yer actions.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:03.76,0:18:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a bird's-eye view of things and turn yer anger and regret into weapons.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:10.13,0:18:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:12.25,0:18:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hishigata, does it mean anything for you to keep quiet any longer?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:17.80,0:18:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Get my daughter.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:20.64,0:18:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring me the real Tokiko.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:32.64,0:18:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you awake?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:35.71,0:18:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sei.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:37.43,0:18:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Where am I?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:42.70,0:18:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave Chitose the same memories I showed ya.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:50.84,0:18:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Chitose.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:53.02,0:18:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sou's mother didn't realize that she was a shadow.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:58.70,0:19:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She was created that way.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:01.88,0:19:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're trying to stop the ceremony,
Dialogue: 5,0:19:06.07,0:19:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but should you really kill Haine?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:10.27,0:19:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:12.13,0:19:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All the shadows will die with Haine.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:15.93,0:19:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That means your Ushio will die too!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:25.43,0:19:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:27.28,0:19:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:29.09,0:19:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've been dead fer two days already.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:31.98,0:19:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm lucky to even have this bonus time being alive.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:37.74,0:19:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can, I want to use the time to help save everyone.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:42.14,0:19:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Defeating Haine will solve everything, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:45.50,0:19:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good news!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:47.51,0:19:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll gladly take her down!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:52.20,0:19:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's right.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:53.45,0:19:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm embarrassed that I even hesitated.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:56.76,0:19:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:57.93,0:19:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:59.47,0:20:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hishigata, what is Haine planning after being revived?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:05.90,0:20:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She just wants to go back home.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:10.43,0:20:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to her hometown, across the deep and dark ocean.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:18.17,0:20:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No being from this world can reach that place,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:22.55,0:20:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,unless it's a shadow.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:25.28,0:20:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Haine wants to just take shadows.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:28.81,0:20:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the family that she chose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.89,0:20:37.59,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}All traces of you vanished into the sea breeze
Dialogue: 5,0:20:32.29,0:20:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But that's...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:34.32,0:20:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible if she regains her power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:42.45,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}But even now I still see visions of you
Dialogue: 5,0:20:38.27,0:20:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a land without time.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:41.52,0:20:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitose and I were going to become shadows and live there forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:50.31,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}In reality I only have vivid memories
Dialogue: 5,0:20:47.13,0:20:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sou and Tokiko were also supposed to join us in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:55.26,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}To play in my head over and over again
Dialogue: 5,0:20:51.97,0:20:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why ya thought it was okay if ya killed us?!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:54.70,0:20:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer so selfish!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:57.43,0:20:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Are ya a fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.57,0:21:00.64,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}Even if it's all just a lie
Dialogue: 5,0:20:58.99,0:21:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:04.30,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}Please be close by my side
Dialogue: 5,0:21:01.34,0:21:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer so self-centered and hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.15,0:21:07.41,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}Right next to me
Dialogue: 5,0:21:09.34,0:21:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks fer saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:13.63,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}I fell for you before too long
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.63,0:21:17.38,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}But time alone was what progressed
Dialogue: 5,0:21:16.04,0:21:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitose...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:17.66,0:21:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But we need to finish this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.99,0:21:21.87,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}I wanna go back
Dialogue: 5,0:21:20.57,0:21:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sou, Tokiko.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:22.95,0:21:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad to have seen ya grow until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.35,0:21:31.03,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}I've listened to my share of heartbreak songs
Dialogue: 5,0:21:27.89,0:21:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Chitose!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:29.93,0:21:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no reason to live if you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.80,0:21:38.69,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}Spending my days torn up and crying but now
Dialogue: 5,0:21:33.84,0:21:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, ya have our children.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:37.58,0:21:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya have the people of this island who need ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:41.34,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}I want to move on
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.78,0:21:46.24,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}I shouldn't act tough and just finally be
Dialogue: 5,0:21:42.47,0:21:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Shinpei said, this ain't over.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:46.71,0:21:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya can still make up fer yer mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.58,0:21:49.55,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}True to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.92,0:21:55.49,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}But it's too late for that
Dialogue: 5,0:22:04.61,0:22:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:08.95,0:22:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the clinic's secret records that Tokiko hid for me.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:13.47,0:22:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Diagnosed with Capgras syndrome, \Nor the local disease of shadow sickness,
Dialogue: 5,0:22:20.81,0:22:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the people on this list are actually \Nthose whom Haine has consumed.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:26.57,0:22:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Your parents' names are on the list, Shinpei.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:31.64,0:22:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But my parents' boat accidentally sank when they were working.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:37.84,0:22:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They found Hiruko's grotto and planned to make it public.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:42.74,0:22:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they were killed.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:44.86,0:22:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It was made to look like an accident.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:47.21,0:22:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Shide killed them, and I switched the bodies to deliver to Haine.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:53.11,0:22:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:54.73,0:22:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is that all ya have to say?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:56.91,0:23:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the true identity of Shide, don't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:01.12,0:23:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:02.51,0:23:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this photograph.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:04.96,0:23:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shide is Haine's protector and the first child she bore.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:11.07,0:23:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,His original name was Hishigata Shidehiko,
Dialogue: 5,0:23:17.81,0:23:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the founder of Hishigata Clinic and its first director.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:24.93,0:23:24.93,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Preview}
